---
/*
  AdUnit — Google AdSense display ad placeholder.

  HOW TO ENABLE:
  1. Apply at https://adsense.google.com and get approved (takes 1–14 days).
  2. In src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro, uncomment the AdSense <script> in <head>
     and replace ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX with your publisher ID.
  3. In this file, uncomment the <ins> block below and replace:
       - data-ad-client  → your publisher ID  (ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX)
       - data-ad-slot    → the ad slot ID from your AdSense dashboard (a 10-digit number)
  4. Deploy. AdSense will start serving ads automatically.
*/
---

<ins
  class="adsbygoogle"
  style="display:block;position:relative;margin:2rem 0;"
  data-ad-client="ca-pub-5868369279571926"
  data-ad-slot="8066491572"
  data-ad-format="auto"
  data-full-width-responsive="true"
></ins>
<script is:inline>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script>
